Description: Leslie West (Mississippi Queen) Signature DeanGuitar, Soltero Minimal use, excellent condition, awesomesounding guitar. The carved, flame maple top sits over the select mahoganybody, adding even more sustain. Super hot USA Dean Leslie West Mountain of Tone"Humbucker Pickup in the bridge position that has the Leslie West/ Mountain /Mississippi Queen tone right out of the box…this is a beauty that roars. Soltero fret board inlays, Grover tuners.Brazilian finish, two-tone sunburst that's amberin the center, fanning out to black at the outer edges; the sides, back andneck are also black.A slightly 'V'-shaped mahogany neck is joinedto the body, dark rosewood fingerboard with pearl, Soltero inlays.Tune-o-matic bridge and separate anchor block,Grover tuners Dean USA Mountain Of Tone Humbucker is a highoutput (16.57k ohms), with an Alnico V magnet. Title: Leslie West, Dean / Soltero Electric Guitar, Excellent Condition, Amazing Tone
